{"tid":752043,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[Minecraft]有冇巴打有性趣一齊玩1.13, 已經開咗server啦! [2]","createTime":"2018-07-22T12:41:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-25T05:03:32.000Z","uid":107458,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"4d07b58819ff7949d495397fe566e2c901f5bee8","tid":752043,"uid":107458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T12:41:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Minecraft  1.13</span> --- <span style=\"color: teal;\"><strong>Update Aquatic</strong></span>  <br />\n更新咗好多嘢 有性趣想搵人一齊玩 己經租左個細Server, <br />\n由零開始慢慢玩 個Server會<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>24小時</strong></span>長開 主要玩基本生存 <br />\n只限<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">正版</span>同埋<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">有白名</span> <br />\n有性趣嘅話就留一留名~ 最緊要係留埋你地 <span style=\"color: gold;\">minecraft 個名</span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <span style=\"color: violet;\">只限正版, 唔包開心版</span>  <br />\n而家暫時係 <strong><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">官方 1.13</span> </strong> 既版本, <br />\n姐係 原生生存 等bukkit更新左之後, <br />\n就會轉番bukkit既1.13,  到時會有plugin, <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">但係唔會玩mod </span>  <br />\n而家己經有discord谷 希望大家入黎discord谷, <br />\n因為詳細既野都會係discord update先 無mic唔緊要, <br />\n可以打字, 用黎gather information  link 在此 : <a href=\"https://discord.gg/ptpacNb\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdiscord.gg%2FptpacNb&d=YI%2FIKu%2Bzxg81hopPUmZUAZWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=a525a658\" target=\"_blank\">https://discord.gg/ptpacNb</a>"},{"pid":"ec8f28eb9396bdf9468033b3f36626ff37e3adde","tid":752043,"uid":107458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T12:44:33.000Z","msg":"不過而家有少少技術性調整<br />\n星期二會正式開放<br />\n大家可以留住名先<br />\n星期二會喺discord公佈 IP"},{"pid":"db1eb2c4ddd9b3114199e3ac70b5c2fe253e0aa4","tid":752043,"uid":66938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0